        "subject": "LU-10499 llite: Add new DLM mode PCCRO for readonly PCC",
        "message": "LU-10499 llite: Add new DLM mode PCCRO for readonly PCC\n\nCurrently Readonly mode of PCC uses grouplock to protect the data\nfrom being written or even normal read from other clients, even\nif there is still a copy on the original OSTs.\nThis patch introduces a new kind of LDLM lock mode PCCRO, which is\ncompatible with PR lock mode, so when the file is PCC-fetched and\nattached on a client, the client will obtain PCCRO lock on the\nfile which allows the read access for the file data on original\nOSTs from other clients, but no write lock is allowed.\n\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: If3076069c77858c9e1572e9fe24cc0af32cabc58\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
